WEBVTT

00:05:29.287 --> 00:05:33.063
These images are from a
Syrian refugee camp in Lebanon

00:05:33.087 --> 00:05:36.207
where lots of children who live there

00:05:36.207 --> 00:05:38.667
have not been able to
go to school for years.

00:05:38.667 --> 00:05:43.347
The science you can feel,
that I was talking about earlier

00:05:43.347 --> 00:05:46.807
will be visible to you
soon in the next image.

00:05:50.127 --> 00:05:55.303
Over one million microscopes
will be sent to every corner of the world.

00:05:55.327 --> 00:05:58.983
With the help of the Department
of Biotechnology in the Indian Government

00:05:59.007 --> 00:06:01.579
a host of these microscopes
will be deployed in India